node.text:
Simon comes to his cat's rescue after discovering him up a tree - meowing for help!

The Tree is a classic example of when life imitates art, then art imitates real life! Simon drew this gag in one of his books, only for it to happen to him in real life a few years later. Ask him, he has the scars to prove it!
